description: I come from a diverse cultural background including South Africa and Canada. I love Georgia Tech and Lambda Chi because they both are very diverse as well. The brothers at Beta Kappa Zeta are the best group of guys I could ever hope to be a part of and I have enjoyed every second of my membership here.
